weeks I was lost in the jungle.

106
00:07:35,357 --> 00:07:38,257
Thought I was going
to die for sure.

107
00:07:38,290 --> 00:07:43,057
Now, we're going to
settle this-- for good!

108
00:07:43,090 --> 00:07:45,490
-I dunno what to
tell you, Ryoga.

109
00:07:45,524 --> 00:07:46,757
-You're damn right.

110
00:07:46,790 --> 00:07:48,557
