to say anything

111
00:07:48,590 --> 00:07:50,857
to me, not after
what you've done.

112
00:07:50,890 --> 00:07:53,090
-That's not what I
meant, you idiot.

113
00:07:53,124 --> 00:07:55,524
-I've heard enough of
your talking already.

114
00:07:55,557 --> 00:07:56,024
