-Hey, I just thought
of something.

127
00:08:43,657 --> 00:08:48,990
If that guy kills Saotome,
then Akane's not a-- you know--

128
00:08:53,457 --> 00:08:55,657
-Not engaged anymore.

129
00:08:55,690 --> 00:08:58,657
