would be free to become--

130
00:08:58,690 --> 00:09:01,424
-Become our chemistry
club's-- well, you know.

131
00:09:01,457 --> 00:09:05,257
[laughter]

132
00:09:05,290 --> 00:09:06,224
-Take this, you coward!

133
00:09:13,457 --> 00:09:15,490
