134
00:09:15,524 --> 00:09:18,724
-These ought to prevent you
from escaping me again, Ranma.

135
00:09:18,757 --> 00:09:22,590
-How many times do I have
to tell I didn't run away?

136
00:09:22,624 --> 00:09:24,590
Huh?

137
00:09:24,624 --> 00:09:26,590
Ha!

138
00:09:26,624 --> 00:09:27,090
-Ugh.

139
00:09:38,090 --> 00:09:39,557
MALE SPECTATOR 1:
Hey, check it out!

140
00:09:39,590 --> 00:09:41,524
