158
00:10:29,124 --> 00:10:30,490
-Silence, wretch!

159
00:10:30,524 --> 00:10:33,857
Do not disturb my meditation.

160
00:10:33,890 --> 00:10:35,857
Ah.

161
00:10:35,890 --> 00:10:38,190
Ah.

162
00:10:38,224 --> 00:10:40,424
Akane!

163
00:10:40,457 --> 00:10:42,157
Pig-tailed girl!

164
00:10:42,190 --> 00:10:44,190
I-I-- no!

165
00:10:44,224 --> 00:10:49,190
Whichever shall I choose?
[shouts] I love them both!

166
00:10:49,224 --> 00:10:50,657
[shouts]

167
