169
00:11:05,805 --> 00:11:06,405
-Hey!

170
00:11:06,438 --> 00:11:07,805
Ranma!

171
00:11:07,838 --> 00:11:11,638
Don't get too close to him!

172
00:11:11,671 --> 00:11:12,871
-Oh, now you get serious.

