175
00:11:23,171 --> 00:11:27,138
-So Ryoga, what should
I do with you now?

176
00:11:27,171 --> 00:11:29,338
-Curse you, Saotome!

177
00:11:29,371 --> 00:11:30,371
-Oh, no!

178
00:11:30,405 --> 00:11:32,405
