W-What's going on?

201
00:13:01,105 --> 00:13:02,938
N-now what are we going to do?

202
00:13:02,971 --> 00:13:04,005
[whimpering]

203
00:13:04,038 --> 00:13:04,938
KEN CLUB MEMBER: Chief.

204
00:13:04,971 --> 00:13:05,705
-What?

205
00:13:05,738 --> 00:13:07,771
-We've got one last resort.

206
00:13:07,805 --> 00:13:10,738
