down the evil Ranma.

215
00:13:35,805 --> 00:13:37,171
-We are here--

216
00:13:37,205 --> 00:13:37,938
-To see that--

217
00:13:37,971 --> 00:13:38,838
-Akane's been made happy--

218
00:13:38,871 --> 00:13:39,571
-So you just--

219
00:13:39,605 --> 00:13:40,571
-Rest in peace, Saotome!

220
00:13:53,138 --> 00:13:54,105
-Over there!

221
00:14:00,005 --> 00:14:01,238
-OK, ladies.

222
00:14:01,271 --> 00:14:02,071
Now it's our turn.

223
00:14:02,105 --> 00:14:02,905
Let's go.

224
00:14:02,938 --> 00:14:04,071
