233
00:14:29,371 --> 00:14:31,805
Take these tablets and your
strength will increase tenfold.

234
00:14:36,805 --> 00:14:38,105
-W-what?

235
00:14:38,138 --> 00:14:38,605
-Here.

236
00:14:44,905 --> 00:14:47,571
You're about to become the
strongest man in the world.

237
00:14:47,605 --> 00:14:51,071
No one will be able to stop you.

238
00:14:51,105 --> 00:14:53,338
Think how do strong,
you'll have no rival.

239
00:14:53,371 --> 00:14:54,305
You're an Atlas!

240
00:14:54,338 --> 00:14:55,905
