compared to you!

241
00:14:55,938 --> 00:14:57,605
You're a tiger, a tiger!

242
00:14:57,638 --> 00:14:58,571
You are a tiger!

243
00:15:02,971 --> 00:15:05,571
-I can feel the strength
flowing through me!

244
00:15:05,605 --> 00:15:06,971
I can feel the power.

245
00:15:07,005 --> 00:15:07,805
I'm burning with it!

246
00:15:07,838 --> 00:15:08,771
I can win.

247
00:15:08,805 --> 00:15:09,571
I can win!

248
00:15:15,838 --> 00:15:17,271
