257
00:15:37,505 --> 00:15:39,071
-Uh, Nibiki.

258
00:15:39,105 --> 00:15:41,671
Those are just vitamin
tablets we gave him, right?

259
00:15:41,705 --> 00:15:42,905
-Mhm.

260
00:15:42,938 --> 00:15:46,471
-The power of suggestion
is truly a thing of wonder.

261
00:15:46,505 --> 00:15:51,671
[chuckle]

262
00:15:51,705 --> 00:15:52,905
RYOGA: Come back here, Ranma!

263
00:15:56,871 --> 00:15:58,652
You won't escape me again!

264
00:16:02,985 --> 00:16:03,652
-Help!

265
00:16:03,685 --> 00:16:06,419
